we've been, um...

1:24:00.244 --> 1:24:02.871
speaking all over the place,
but our writing,

1:24:02.871 --> 1:24:05.082
at least my writing,
about the movement

1:24:05.082 --> 1:24:06.166
never gets published.

1:24:06.416 --> 1:24:08.460
-Does that happen to you?
-[women chuckle]

1:24:09.211 --> 1:24:11.380
Maybe, um, maybe we should

1:24:11.880 --> 1:24:13.799
have some kind
of a newsletter, right?

1:24:14.091 --> 1:24:15.133
