the movement.

1:24:30.148 --> 1:24:31.191
Can't worry about that.

1:24:31.525 --> 1:24:34.444
Look, I can't get a single story
about a real woman

1:24:34.444 --> 1:24:36.238
published in magazines
run by men.

1:24:36.238 --> 1:24:38.365
