1:28:10.202 --> 1:28:12.913
Thousands do it,
it's a movement.

1:28:13.788 --> 1:28:16.124
Are we gonna do this for real?

1:28:16.416 --> 1:28:19.461
We have to... right?

1:28:19.461 --> 1:28:23.048
Baby, we got to stop sucking,
