-[laughs]

2:07:18.673 --> 2:07:19.757
[Gloria]
The airport, please.

2:07:19.757 --> 2:07:21.175
...on Glen's lap.

2:07:23.594 --> 2:07:25.429
[man over radio] Hey, speaking
of the shootings in Whittleton,

2:07:25.847 --> 2:07:27.265
did those kids try and have sex

2:07:27.265 --> 2:07:28.891
with any of those
good-looking girls first?

2:07:28.891 --> 2:07:30.560
-[woman over radio] Hmm.
-At least if you're gonna kill

2:07:30.560 --> 2:07:31.727
yourself and kill
all the kids...

2:07:32.228 --> 2:07:33.771
-Can you please turn that off?
-Why didn't you have some sex?

2:07:33.771 --> 2:07:35.231
[woman over radio]
He got pretty far away...

2:07:35.231 --> 2:07:36.357
[brake squeals]

2:07:36.357 --> 2:07:38.359
-[men clamoring]
-Dirty lazy people.

2:07:38.734 --> 2:07:41.612
[speaking in foreign language]

2:07:41.612 --> 2:07:42.697
Please.

2:07:43.030 --> 2:07:45.032
-Stop yelling.
-[continues in foreign language]

2:07:46.993 --> 2:07:49.120
-I crash you.
-[car horn honking]

2:07:49.120 --> 2:07:50.580
-You know--
-I crash you.

2:07:50.580 --> 2:07:52.999
You know, some people
in this country

2:07:53.666 --> 2:07:55.668
think bad things
about immigrants

2:07:55.668 --> 2:07:57.253
-from Russia and they're wrong.
-Are you crazy?

2:07:57.253 --> 2:07:59.005
I'm from Ukraine, not Russia.

2:07:59.005 --> 2:08:01.340
Ukraine is good place.
Everybody wait.

2:08:01.340 --> 2:08:03.551
-No dirty people--
-If there are no people of color

2:08:03.551 --> 2:08:05.177
in Ukraine then why are you

2:08:05.177 --> 2:08:06.637
making assumptions
about anything?

2:08:06.637 --> 2:08:09.432
You know nothing.
Black peoples ruin this country.

2:08:10.474 --> 2:08:12.310
-[brake squeals]
-[woman screams]

2:08:12.310 --> 2:08:14.103
-[horn honking]
-[speaking foreign language]

2:08:14.103 --> 2:08:16.188
-Fucking bitch!
-You know what?

2:08:16.188 --> 2:08:20.484
That's it. Pull over. I've had
it with your racist bullshit.

2:08:20.484 --> 2:08:23.070
The reason this country is great
is that all of these people,

2:08:23.070 --> 2:08:25.698
black, brown, white,
all of these beautiful people

2:08:25.698 --> 2:08:27.575
are on the streets
in New York together.

2:08:27.575 --> 2:08:29.577
And if you don't like
living in New York

2:08:29.577 --> 2:08:32.121
then you can just move
to fucking Norway!

2:09:31.597 --> 2:09:33.099
[woman] A dear friend of mine.

2:09:33.766 --> 2:09:37.019
We met almost 40 years ago
right here in Deli.

2:09:37.436 --> 2:09:40.523
A place where she began her
journey as an activist.

2:09:41.899 --> 2:09:44.235
The greatest listener
on this planet.

2:09:44.527 --> 2:09:48.572
She has lovingly been called
a celestial bartender.

2:09:48.572 --> 2:09:50.116
[audience laughing]

2:09:50.116 --> 2:09:53.911
Today, we are honored to be able
to listen to Gloria herself

2:09:54.203 --> 2:09:56.038
read from her new book.

2:09:59.000 --> 2:10:00.876
"Men embody adventure.

2:10:00.876 --> 2:10:02.962
Women embody hearth and home

2:10:02.962 --> 2:10:04.755
and that has been
pretty much it.

2:10:06.215 --> 2:10:10.261
Even as a child, I noticed that
Dorothy in the Wizard of Oz

2:10:10.261 --> 2:10:12.847
spent her entire time trying
to get back home to Kansas.

2:10:13.097 --> 2:10:16.642
Um. Alice in Wonderland
dreamed her long adventure

2:10:16.934 --> 2:10:19.103
and woke up just in time
for tea. [chuckles]

2:10:19.103 --> 2:10:19.979
[audience chuckles]

2:10:20.271 --> 2:10:24.358
But... whether by dowry murders
in India,

2:10:25.109 --> 2:10:26.902
honor killings in Egypt,

2:10:27.570 --> 2:10:30.281
or domestic violence
in the United States,

2:10:30.865 --> 2:10:35.286
statistically speaking, home is
an even more dangerous place

2:10:35.286 --> 2:10:36.746
for women than the road.

2:10:38.039 --> 2:10:39.248
Taking to the road,

2:10:39.498 --> 2:10:42.084
by which I mean letting the road
take you,

2:10:43.002 --> 2:10:44.587
changed who I thought I was.

2:10:45.880 --> 2:10:49.383
The road is messy in the way
that real life is messy.

2:10:50.051 --> 2:10:52.970
It leads us out of denial
and into reality.

2:10:53.471 --> 2:10:55.681
Out of theory and into practice.

2:10:55.931 --> 2:10:59.143
Out of caution and into action.

2:10:59.894 --> 2:11:03.189
Out of statistics and into
stories.

2:11:03.189 --> 2:11:06.317
In short, out of our heads
and into our hearts."

2:11:09.153 --> 2:11:11.197
[speaking foreign language]

2:11:26.337 --> 2:11:27.379
Now...

2:11:28.464 --> 2:11:30.800
be partners forever.

2:11:31.675 --> 2:11:33.135
That's the way it'll be.

2:11:36.806 --> 2:11:38.974
So what happened to you,
Miss Feminist,

2:11:38.974 --> 2:11:42.561
who used to say marriage
turns women into half people?

2:11:42.561 --> 2:11:44.396
-[laughs]
-You were fucking 66 years old.

2:11:44.647 --> 2:11:46.524
